"3 pounds flat-cut beef brisket, trimmed and cut into 1-inch cubes","1 pound beef stew meat","2 teaspoons freshly ground black pepper, divided","1 3/4 teaspoons kosher salt, divided","5 teaspoons canola oil, divided","4 cups chopped yellow onion","2 tablespoons dried oregano","1 1/2 tablespoons paprika","1 tablespoon chili powder","1 tablespoon ancho chile powder","1 tablespoon ground cumin","6  garlic cloves, finely chopped","2  dried bay leaves","1  dried ancho chile, seeded","1  (6-ounce) can unsalted tomato paste","4 1/2 cups water, divided","1  (12-ounce) lager beer (such as Shiner)","5 tablespoons masa harina","2 teaspoons hot sauce (such as Tabasco)","1/2 cup chopped green onions"